PrecisAmendments to the IMMIGRATION ACT FEES REGULATIONS which raise the fees for eight immigration services and introduce two new fees, one for a multiple- entry Visitor Visa ($75) and one for the replacement of a lost or expired Permanent Resident Card ($40), effective April 1, 1993 (Cost-recovery - Phase V).
